Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼所在的三號殖民地\n柯西3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.46,0:01:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了潛入那裏\n我們先進入一座礦山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.83,0:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是姬娜在那裏\n波蕾二世也到那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連反抗哈曼的勞動者都有\n柯亞之行差點沒指望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.23,0:01:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是礦山隕石奇凱洛\n之所以能與柯亞3的接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.45,0:01:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為哈曼在呼喚我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.70,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十三話\n柯亞3的少女 後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.19,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯亞3,是三號殖民地\n空域的中央殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.77,0:02:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地球聯邦政府送給哈曼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門打開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.86,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛亂份子高達隊伍\n就躲在奇凱洛裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.81,0:02:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他們一個不漏的捉出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛亂份子的根據地在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.83,0:02:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.27,0:02:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出來可免去勞役的\n你想回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.77,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃走了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這一帶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.54,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾出去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.29,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.04,0:03:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道這裏是美莉芭殿下的房間\n還敢闖進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美莉芭.沙比?\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰敢反抗就開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美莉芭.沙比殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再做出奇怪的舉動\n我就槍殺你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准再發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.58,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪麗的小羊呢?\n吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.14,0:04:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅伊,你沒事吧?\n那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅伊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道情況了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.34,0:04:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一第二空氣鎖\以及十三礦坑有自護兵在防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四空氣鎖呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.92,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,z高達和zz高達還在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯  問出下落馬上就能搶回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅伊,你知道哈曼在哪裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.19,0:04:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在他們徵收了\n山手線上的老百姓別墅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用新亞加瑪的\n超級米加粒子炮瞄準哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯亞3有五百萬的市民阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.55,0:04:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉和露卡\n還有露姿娜都在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿  新亞加瑪的\n超級米加粒子炮能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明告訴我你的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.28,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把臉抬起來吧,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.17,0:05:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你與波蕾是雙胞胎的姐妹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認識波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.29,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是古利明教你的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小事,我自己會學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.03,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你那麼自信\n好強的氣勢,在這裏不能動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著我要命令你去\n鎮壓奇凱洛的叛亂份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了,姬娜\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼伊,藍斯\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的古利明\n居然派強化人來接近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔掉奇凱洛和柯亞3\n的合體部份沒有問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.02,0:05:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會危害到\n奇凱洛與柯亞3的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.63,0:05:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是不相信你,但...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧,捷度\n拜託你了,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很擔心露姿娜吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.49,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也很擔心艾莉和露卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\n我是個不負責任的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.65,0:06:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,在新亞加瑪過來之前\n發現自衛兵就把他們趕出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,趁現在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要走了,捷度,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了來了,來一大堆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,該動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.48,0:06:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.75,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,動手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.77,0:06:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離新亞加瑪還很遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會被打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.65,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認真的嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到這裏一口氣\n便可飛到新亞加瑪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我撐不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個隕石,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼  成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度和伊萊\n不知有沒有順利成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,因為我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個太細了\n露卡,你有沒有帶什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算打開了\n外面還有衛兵把守著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些男人\n憑我的魅力一定可以擺平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我在做體操啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准帶她走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.43,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想來幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再反抗的話\n這次真的會打中她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等啊,我走就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,過來\n露姿娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.62,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼在這裏停下來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在這裏會死掉的,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只救我ㄧ個?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.61,0:09:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有兄弟姐妹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,我家只有我和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.12,0:09:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要救的話\n也要救艾莉和露卡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想其他人了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.13,0:09:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不想死的話就快點離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你為什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.77,0:09:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩是波蕾二世的同伴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示她是古利明的手下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.88,0:09:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管她\n我比較在意那個小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...  少囉唆!\n我可是隊長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長,那女孩...\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她又回北方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看,我的判斷沒錯吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧,尼伊,藍斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是成功潛入了,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是羅伊所說的別墅嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該怎麼辦\n才能救出露姿娜她們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,艾莉和露卡呢??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們被關在那邊的地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是怎樣出來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.87,0:10:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是波蕾二世救我出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.98,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我不希望只有自己得救\所以又折回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她只救了你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次換成捷度過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.71,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道高達隊伍和叛亂份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.43,0:10:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是古利明在背後控制的??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧\n是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,一定是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妄想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.63,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把槍放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說不准動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,你快清醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.77,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.99,0:10:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我說要注意波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼,你要去哪裏?\n這裏不准任意行動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也駕駛MS應戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.62,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼,你覺悟吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.74,0:11:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然露出真面目了\n否則剛才不會有那股壓力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把美莉芭殿下帶去安全地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.06,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受命去討伐亞加瑪的古利明\n對亞古捷斯發動襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明攻擊亞古捷斯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.67,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙終於忍不住\n犯下魯莽的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓亞古捷斯被擊落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命,那恐怕是遲早的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把全部戰力招集到港口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.93,0:12:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到我\n她什麼力量也使不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.47,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你能永遠玩弄我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會大話的女人\n做的到什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做事太多破綻了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算她駕駛的是卡碧尼\n遭到我蓋馬魯古的一齊掃射照樣是撐不住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,請停手\n柯亞3會崩潰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.58,0:12:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人和美莉芭殿下\n還在府邸裏面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.24,0:13:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?你們不給我機會\n展現蓋亞魯古的性能嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們做事太不智了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太小看我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.35,0:13:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在殖民地內部用MS戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是捷度來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不太可能這樣大打出手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.23,0:13:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人在附近我才手下留情\n我再也忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,這裏無法過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.91,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走這邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.31,0:13:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明\n你以為我沒想到你可能造反嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道理由,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡碧尼突然襲擊哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上吧!把吉翁兵趕出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開槍!開槍阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.10,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來人!放我們出去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想死在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,露卡\n是捷度的聲音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,艾莉,你們沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退後,我要擊壞門鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!你果然來救我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,我好不容易與你感動重逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\n你在說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你阿,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.83,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你在府邸設下防護罩的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.34,0:15:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指我們的精神力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.42,0:15:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是精神力還是什麼力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.27,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你,我們不會\n連一個卡碧尼也反應不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.18,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓開吧,新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的波蕾二世,你惹火我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,美莉芭殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.05,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人與美莉芭殿下還在裏面\n帶她們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有存心做什麼\n這是情勢自己演變的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.71,0:16:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過,你與我都是同類\n我們在互相呼喚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.57,0:16:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度根本就不會殺小孩\n你太糊塗了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.93,0:16:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,請快上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍斯嗎?辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我就放你一馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到港口的沙達朗去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.08,0:16:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.85,0:16:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快到了,加油,就在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是便利車的車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搭乘便利車是逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時刻不會有車開的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看一片漆黑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我們抱著必死的決心過來\n竟然沒人迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些MS全部跑到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.64,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是比查和莫迪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,奇凱洛怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吉翁兵已經撤到合體灣口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的只等新亞加碼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,你解開便利車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.45,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一言難盡呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死人的嘍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.33,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到會在這裏見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.54,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫迪,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.50,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,快給我駕駛ZZ高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.19,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,是這樣玩的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算精神器較少...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一個我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.06,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你想被殺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.03,0:18:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別逞強了\n剛才你為何心情動搖?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要救露姿娜?波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.39,0:18:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死波蕾令你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.65,0:18:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你才救露姿娜\n想彌補那個愧疚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少自以為是吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.34,0:18:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然你說吧\n為何只救露姿娜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.12,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把波蕾投射在露姿娜身上\n不,是把你自己重疊在她身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.01,0:19:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會...我沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你陷害我,捷度,你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒那個意思的,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只要正視自己的心\n就不會痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一點也不痛苦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼能逃過全面攻擊的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓自己更誠實點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是壞女孩阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才不瞭解我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.37,0:19:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超級米加粒子炮,準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開瞄準器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間到了,撤退吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.21,0:19:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,主炮發射時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,快離開這空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又要騙我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是,有危險阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.29,0:20:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源到達臨界點了\n超級米加粒子炮,準備發射!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超級米加粒子炮,發射!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.02,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個震動是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.37,0:20:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇凱絡的合體灣口\n被強力的米加粒子炮貫穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加碼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我駕駛蓋馬魯古出擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓波蕾二世逃走是我一大恥辱\n我想挽回名譽阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管她\n損失一個礦山隕石不算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當前第一要務是收拾古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.55,0:21:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,這艦隊就交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去鎮壓造反的古利明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.04,0:21:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,幸好你沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.30,0:21:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,讓你受了那麼多苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是爸爸不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.50,0:21:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸救了大家\n爸爸很偉大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.48,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,奇凱洛的各位能獲得自由\n都是捷度他們的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不知該如何向你們道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.00,0:21:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是出手幫個忙而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有幫忙阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.05,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.65,0:21:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好奇凱洛還有\n可供暫時生活的空氣食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會移往到別的殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露姿娜,你要好好珍惜爸爸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.52,0:22:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,波蕾二世不是壞孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.24,0:22:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,我知道的,露姿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.37,0:23:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明和姬娜的艦隊的攻擊開始了\n這對於我們來說是一個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.30,0:23:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我把柯亞3的米涅芭·扎比捉為人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.01,0:23:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 那只是我的一己之見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.99,0:23:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪反而陷入了危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.49,0:24:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此時 作為盾牌救了亞加瑪的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.40,0:24:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.73,0:24:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉的犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.82,0:24:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都說這太勉強了！

